temperature kam karne se answers zyada precise aate hain
temperature badhane se answers zyada creative aate hain
0.2 thick chal raha hai tool calling ke liye

llama ke models mei jitna data jayda hota hai utna bekar vo perform karta hai
qwen ke model bade data pe ache perform karte hain

qwen ke model tool calling bhi bhot acha karte hain
llama ke model mei tool calling thodi weak hai and dont recommended for use


